com.ibm.streams.beam.sdk.io

Interface SwiftFileSystemOptions

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HasDisplayData, PipelineOptions

    public interface SwiftFileSystemOptions
extends PipelineOptions
    Options used to configure IBM Cloud Object Storage Swift.

    The user id, password, project ID, and region are required options if the swift:// scheme is used.
